ssion for this group.\\n\\n\\nI don't see a session for the QLHV group in the current sessions list, and since sessions_send only works with existing sessions, I need to find another way to reach the group directly through Telegram instead.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_w6o3p8icr7de_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"limit\": 10,\n                \"messageLimit\": 1\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 152,\n            \"output\": 226,\n            \"totalTokens\": 18441,\n            \"cacheRead\": 16346,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 1717,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776183365798,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d9b464c0108c321d04a4981987150\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"7a1e771c\",\n            \"seq\": 9\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776183224951,\n      \"sessionId\": \"19b78d16-3e00-45ff-9064-232cca762111\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 45140,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776180724499,\n   